data.title: Xperia P, Xperia U, and Xperia sola driver
data.text:
Phone drivers for Xperia P (LT22i), Sony Xperia U (ST25a and ST25i), and Sony Xperia sola (MT27i) running the Android Gingerbread version. Use drivers for debugging, or when erased from phone.

| 8.29 Mb

Xperia_P_Xperia_U_Xperia_sola_drivers.zip
